                  </persName>
            . I am a publican. The prosecutor and a woman came and had some gin - I cannot swear to the prisoner; I gave him change for half a sovereign.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18300916-309-person2538">
                  ROBERT 
                  TURLE
               <interp inst="t18300916-309-person2538" type="surname" value="TURLE"></interp>
