                     <interp inst="t18300916-309-person2538" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a Policeman. I saw the prosecutor and prisoner disputing: I went up, and he gave her in charge for stealing 2s. 6d. from his pocket - she denied it; no money was found on her.</p>
